{
  "uid": "peepbot-data",
  "title": "Peep Bot — Data Layer",
  "tags": ["peepbot", "data"],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "timezone": "browser",
  "editable": false,
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "datasource",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": { "text": "Prometheus", "value": "prometheus" },
        "hide": 0
      },
      {
        "name": "service",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(application_ready_time_milliseconds{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\"}, service_name)",
        "refresh": 1,
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": { "text": "peepbot-backend", "value": "peepbot-backend" }
      },
      {
        "name": "env",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(application_ready_time_milliseconds{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\"}, deployment_environment_name)",
        "refresh": 1,
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": { "text": "production", "value": "production" }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "HikariCP Active",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(hikaricp_connections_active{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"})"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "value"
      },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "decimals": 0 } }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "HikariCP Idle",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 4, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(hikaricp_connections_idle{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"})"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "value"
      },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "decimals": 0 } }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "HikariCP Pending",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 9, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(hikaricp_connections_pending{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"})"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "value"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "HikariCP Max",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 14, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(hikaricp_connections_max{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"})"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "graphMode": "none",
        "colorMode": "value"
      },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "decimals": 0 } }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "HikariCP Timeouts /s",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 19, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(hikaricp_connections_timeout_total{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"}[5m]))"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "value"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 2,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0 }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Connection wait & usage (p95)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(hikaricp_connections_acquire_milliseconds_bucket{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"}[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "acquire p95"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(hikaricp_connections_usage_milliseconds_bucket{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"}[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "usage p95"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(hikaricp_connections_creation_milliseconds_bucket{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"}[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "creation p95"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ms" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "JDBC commits vs rollbacks",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(jdbc_connection_commit_total{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "commits/s"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "sum(rate(jdbc_connection_rollback_total{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "rollbacks/s"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "short" },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "rollbacks/s" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" } }]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Per-repository latency",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (repository) (rate(spring_data_repository_invocations_milliseconds_count{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"}[5m]))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, repository) (rate(spring_data_repository_invocations_milliseconds_bucket{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"}[5m])))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        { "id": "joinByField", "options": { "byField": "repository", "mode": "outer" } },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time 1": true,
              "Time 2": true
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "repository": "Repository",
              "Value #A": "calls/s",
              "Value #B": "p95 (ms)"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "sortBy",
          "options": {
            "fields": {},
            "sort": [{ "field": "p95 (ms)", "desc": true }]
          }
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": [
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "calls/s" }, "properties": [{ "id": "unit", "value": "short" }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "p95 (ms)" }, "properties": [{ "id": "unit", "value": "ms" }] }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Sessions Active",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 22 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(tomcat_sessions_active_current{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"})"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "value"
      },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "decimals": 0 } }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Sessions Created/s",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 22 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(tomcat_sessions_created_total{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"}[5m]))"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "value"
      },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "decimals": 2 } }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Sessions Rejected/s",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 22 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(tomcat_sessions_rejected_total{service_namespace=\"peep-bot\", service_name=~\"$service\", deployment_environment_name=~\"$env\"}[5m]))"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "value"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 2,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0 }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Postgres (server-side) — gated on Prereq F",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 26 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Postgres server-side metrics are gated on spec Prereq F.**\n\nThe OTel collector's `postgres` receiver is configured but not currently emitting metrics (e.g. `postgresql_backends`, `postgresql_commits`, `postgresql_rollbacks`, `postgresql_db_size`, `postgresql_bgwriter_*`). Until that is fixed, database health is observed indirectly through HikariCP (connection pool) and `datasource-micrometer` (JDBC commits/rollbacks/queries) panels on this dashboard.\n\nWhen Prereq F lands, add panels for:\n- `postgresql_backends` (active connections, server-side)\n- `rate(postgresql_commits[5m])` vs `rate(postgresql_rollbacks[5m])`\n- `postgresql_db_size` per database\n- `rate(postgresql_bgwriter_buffers_writes[5m])` by source\n- Cache hit ratio: `postgresql_blocks_read{source=\"heap_hit\"} / (heap_hit + heap_read)`"
      },
      "description": "Gated on spec Prereq F — OTel postgres receiver is not yet emitting metrics."
    }
  ]
}
